Many SLAs require that a customer be contacted regularly on a certain period with an update on an issue. For example, every 30 minutes until the issue is resolved.

It would be good to have this ability, or at least to set up an SLA to remind agents that a response is due. The ability to add information to the canned updates would be a bonus.

Currently there doesn't seem to be a trivial way to do this, but it doesn't seem like a big ask.

